room_title: Escape room "Curse of the Crimson Eye" by Mind Games in Roseau
room_description: Gather your crew matey. There's treasure to be found in these waters, that is if your brave enough to challenge the curse of the Crimson Eye.  Can you figure out the clues to escape an ancient pirate curse and rediscover the legendary lost treasure? Jump aboard this high seas adventure in search of fame and fortune,  but heed this warning, thars pirates in these waters.
